    <string name="donate_h1">Dish runs on coffee and goodwill.</string>
    <string name="donate_lead">Dish, Satellite, and every Dish client are free, open source, ad-free, and analytics-free. No paywalled features, no upsells, and no plans for any of that. Donations are what keep them true.</string>
